Common.Highlight.Common.Text: 13km from the heart of the Brisbane CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Situated within 13km from the heart of the Brisbane CBD, 33 Success Street benefits generous access to south east Queensland’s major arterial links being the Ipswich Motorway, Beaudesert Road, Pacific Highway and Centenary Highway. Features of the property include: 

•	870sqm office/warehouse 
•	High bay warehouse accessed via container height roller door  
•	Ground floor showroom and office accommodation 
•	Good truck access via double crossover 
•	Corporate appeal 
•	12 on site car spaces 

For further information, or to arrange an inspection please contact exclusive agent Jack Hardy from CBRE.

18 Paradise Road, Acacia Ridge is situated 12km south from the Brisbane CBD and benefits generous access to south east Queensland’s major arterial links being the Ipswich Motorway, Beaudesert Road, Pacific Highway and Centenary Highway. 
 
Features of the property include:

- 5,071sqm* Industrial Facility with significant concrete hardstand 
- 4,400sqm* warehouse with up to 8.7m* internal height 
- Warehouse access via 2 x 11m* wide container height roller doors 
- 17,860sqm* site area with drive through and around capability 
- Wash bays, workshop, three phase power and spray booth 
 - Rare low site cover option in tightly held Acacia Ridge Industrial Precinct
